packets.name: Floating Tire "precious pink"
packets.author: Pixls
packets.description: Annoyed by all those gigantic floating unicorns, flamingos, and slices of pizza that take up all the space at your local pool? We have the perfect alternative for you: our floating tire in precious pink is minimalistic elegance that can be used to lounge in the pool, on the lawn or even in your own living room! Made from especially durable voxels with a high percentage of anti-fading particles so the sun can't harm the colour. Relax in style this summer with Lorex for PIXL (pixls.eth | ethical blockchain fashion from Austria). Manufactured with MagicaVoxel.
